aims-os-bigdata (2.0) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Carved out of aims-os-math to align with the AIMS
    Coop Big Data filière. Depends on aims-os-math so installing it on
    a vanilla Debian Trixie pulls the full SciPy / R / LaTeX baseline.
    Big Data layer: python3-dask + python3-distributed.
    NLP layer: python3-nltk (spaCy / gensim / transformers stay
    install-on-demand via pipx/mamba).
    Computer Vision: python3-opencv (scikit-image is in aims-os-math).
    Climate sciences: python3-xarray, python3-netcdf4, python3-cartopy.
    Database course: postgresql-client, mariadb-client, redis-tools,
    python3-psycopg2, python3-pymongo.

